    // ── Guide (Researcher) ────────────────────────────────────────────
    'guide.r.title': 'Researcher Guide',
    'guide.r.sub': 'Learn how to get the best quotes with BidVibe.',
    'guide.r.conceptTitle': 'How does BidVibe work?',
    'guide.r.conceptDesc': 'Traditionally, buying reagents, consumables, or equipment meant contacting each supplier individually. BidVibe flips that. Post one request and suppliers compete to submit bids. Researchers use it completely free.',
    'guide.r.conceptTag': 'Supplier competition → lower prices, faster delivery',
    'guide.r.stepsTitle': 'Getting Started — 4 Steps',
    'guide.r.step1Title': 'Search Substance',
    'guide.r.step1Desc': 'Type a CAS number or substance name and get autocomplete from the PubChem database. Substances not in the database can be entered manually.',
    'guide.r.step1Tip': 'Enter 64-17-5 → Ethanol autocomplete',
    'guide.r.step2Title': 'Post Quote Request',
    'guide.r.step2Desc': 'Enter quantity, purity, deadline, and post. Multiple items can be bundled into one bulk request.',
    'guide.r.step2Tip': 'Qty · Unit · Purity · Deadline · Address → Preview → Post',
    'guide.r.step3Title': 'Wait for Supplier Bids',
    'guide.r.step3Desc': 'After posting, suppliers submit competing bids. Bid prices are sealed until the deadline. You get an email notification when a new bid arrives.',
    'guide.r.step3Tip': 'Bid count visible / price revealed after award',
    'guide.r.step4Title': 'Compare and Accept',
    'guide.r.step4Desc': 'Compare delivery time, terms, and supplier reputation, then choose the best offer. Supplier contact info is revealed immediately on acceptance.',
    'guide.r.step4Tip': 'Compare price, delivery, and reliability',
    'guide.r.stepsCta': 'Post Your First Request',
    'guide.r.bulkTitle': 'Bulk Quote Request',
    'guide.r.bulkDesc': 'Use this when requesting multiple items at once. Suppliers can bid on all or some items, and you compare using a price matrix.',
    'guide.r.bulk1Title': 'Manual Entry',
    'guide.r.bulk1Desc': 'Add rows on screen and enter items one by one.',
    'guide.r.bulk2Title': 'Excel Upload',
    'guide.r.bulk2Desc': 'Download the template, fill in items, then upload the file.',
    'guide.r.rulesTitle': 'Good Rules to Know',
    'guide.r.rule1Title': 'Sealed Bid Pricing',
    'guide.r.rule1Desc': "You cannot see other suppliers' prices during bidding. Only the accepted supplier's price is revealed. This prevents collusion among suppliers.",
    'guide.r.rule2Title': 'Transactions Outside Platform',
    'guide.r.rule2Desc': 'BidVibe handles quote matching only. Orders, payments, and delivery are handled directly with the supplier. No commission fees.',
    'guide.r.rule3Title': 'Completely Free for Researchers',
    'guide.r.rule3Desc': 'Posting requests, comparing, accepting, and chatting are all free. Only suppliers pay a subscription.',
    'guide.r.faqTitle': 'FAQ',
    'guide.r.faq1q': 'The substance is not showing up in search.',
    'guide.r.faq1a': 'The substance may not be in PubChem or the CAS number may be incorrect. You can enter the substance name manually.',
    'guide.r.faq2q': 'What happens if no bids come in?',
    'guide.r.faq2a': 'The request automatically expires after the deadline. You can adjust the terms and repost.',
    'guide.r.faq3q': 'Can I cancel after accepting?',
    'guide.r.faq3a': 'Cancellation after acceptance must be negotiated directly with the supplier. The platform facilitates contact exchange.',
    'guide.r.faq4q': "I can't see the bid price.",
    'guide.r.faq4a': "That's normal. Prices are sealed until the deadline in Sealed Bid mode. The accepted supplier's price is revealed after you choose.",
    // ── Guide (Supplier) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    'guide.s.title': 'Supplier Guide',
    'guide.s.sub': 'Learn how to acquire new clients on BidVibe.',
    'guide.s.conceptTitle': 'What is a BidVibe Supplier?',
    'guide.s.conceptDesc': 'You bid directly on quote requests for reagents, consumables, and equipment posted by researchers. Acquire new clients from the platform without cold calling. Only subscribed suppliers can bid; during Stage 1 it is completely free.',
    'guide.s.conceptTag': 'Researchers request first — suppliers just bid',
    'guide.s.stepsTitle': 'Getting Started — 4 Steps',
    'guide.s.step1Title': 'Sign Up & Business Verification',
    'guide.s.step1Desc': 'Enter your business registration number and it is verified in real time via the tax authority API. Only active businesses may register. The first 50 companies get a free 6-month Pro early-bird benefit.',
    'guide.s.step1Tip': 'Enter 10-digit business number → Verify → Registration complete',
    'guide.s.step2Title': 'Profile & Category Setup',
    'guide.s.step2Desc': 'Set the categories you handle and the regions you can deliver to. Only requests matching your categories and regions appear in the marketplace.',
    'guide.s.step2Tip': 'Settings → check categories & regions → Save',
    'guide.s.step3Title': 'Submit Quote in Marketplace',
    'guide.s.step3Desc': 'Find requests matching your categories in the marketplace. Enter unit price, delivery date, and terms to submit a bid. For bulk requests, you can bid on selected items only.',
    'guide.s.step3Tip': 'Click request → Submit quote → Done',
    'guide.s.step4Title': 'Award Notification & Trade',
    'guide.s.step4Desc': 'When a researcher accepts your quote, you receive an instant email notification. Researcher contact info is revealed and you proceed with the order directly.',
    'guide.s.step4Tip': 'Award → Email alert → Contact revealed → Direct trade',
    'guide.s.stepsCta': 'Set Up Profile',
    'guide.s.tipsTitle': 'Bidding Strategy Tips',
    'guide.s.tip1Title': 'Fast Response Wins',
    'guide.s.tip1Desc': 'The sooner you bid after a request is posted, the more visible you are to the researcher. Keep notifications on.',
    'guide.s.tip2Title': 'Be Clear on Terms',
    'guide.s.tip2Desc': 'Specifying delivery guarantees, certificates, and minimum order quantities increases your chance of winning.',
    'guide.s.tip3Title': 'Reviews Build Trust',
    'guide.s.tip3Desc': 'Reviews left by researchers after a completed deal are shown as a trust indicator. A great first impression leads to repeat business.',
    'guide.s.tip4Title': 'Use Market Reference Price',
    'guide.s.tip4Desc': "Refer to the platform's market reference prices to set a competitive unit price.",
    'guide.s.plansTitle': 'Subscription Plans',
    'guide.s.plansNote': 'Pricing is TBD during the early-bird period and will be announced at launch.',
    'guide.s.plansCta': 'Manage Subscription',
    'guide.s.planColPlan': 'Plan',
    'guide.s.planColPrice': 'Monthly',
    'guide.s.planColBid': 'Bids',
    'guide.s.planColApi': 'API',
    'guide.s.planFreePrice': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planFreeBid': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planBasicPrice': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planBasicBid': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planProPrice': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planProBid': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planEntPrice': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.planEntBid': 'TBD',
    'guide.s.faqTitle': 'FAQ',
    'guide.s.faq1q': 'What if I bid but do not win?',
    'guide.s.faq1a': 'Bids expire automatically after the deadline. There is no penalty and you can bid on other requests anytime.',
    'guide.s.faq2q': 'Can I supply only some items in a bulk request?',
    'guide.s.faq2a': 'Yes. You can select only the items you can supply and submit a partial bid.',
    'guide.s.faq3q': 'Business number verification is failing.',
    'guide.s.faq3a': 'Suspended or closed businesses cannot register. Check your business status with the tax authority.',
    'guide.s.faq4q': 'Does changing categories affect existing bids?',
    'guide.s.faq4a': 'No. Existing bids are unaffected. The filter applies only to requests posted after the change.',
